  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dd3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dab \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca 4\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "4 dead in Indiana mall shooting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "At least four people, including the shooter, have died in a shooting that took place at the Greenwood Park mall in Indianapolis, Indiana, United States of America.",
        "According to the police, two other Poodles were injured in the incident.",
        "Indiana State Police told reporters that the mass shooter who opened fire inside a restaurant at the Greenwood Park Mall was also killed.",
        "The shooter's motive is not yet known, but the shooter was armed with a rifle and several magazines.",
        "People who were inside the mall at the time of the shooting told the media that they heard 20 gunshots inside the restaurant."
      ],
